Use HD44780 LCD Module to monitor Raspberry Pi.
For now - display informations from MPD daemon, load.

Building
========
Requirements:
 * GoLang
 * Libraries (go get):

   * gompd (http://github.com/turbowookie/gompd/mpd)
   * gpio (http://github.com/davecheney/gpio)

Building:
 * go get .
 * `make` or `make build_pi` for RaspberryPi

Running
=======

Local (without lcd/gpio): ./rpilcd -console=true

With gpio (on RPI) - require sudo.

Options
-------
 * `-mpdHost=pi:6600` - address:port mpd daemon


